OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772651487
OL,3,CSouth East set to receive millions of
OL,4,Cpounds in funding to help Kinship
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FTwo areas in the South East have been
OL,8,Fselected to receive millions of pounds
OL,9,Fin funding to help Kinship carers.
OL,11,FMedway and Thurrock have been named as
OL,12,FKinship Zones by the government - a
OL,13,Fpilot scheme aimed at supporting
OL,14,Ffamilies looking after vulnerable
OL,15,Fchildren that would have otherwise
OL,16,Fgone into care.
OL,18,FFamilies will receive an allowance of
OL,19,Fup to #300 per week, in line with
OL,20,Ffoster carers, for the first time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
