PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772651487
OL,3,CSouth East set to receive millions of
OL,4,Cpounds in funding to help Kinship
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FSome charities say it'll be life-
OL,8,Fchanging, but many carers will miss
OL,9,Fout.
OL,11,FOne grandmother from the South East
OL,12,Fbecame a kinship carer to her daughter
OL,13,FFrancesca's children after she died
OL,14,Fsuddenly six years ago.
OL,16,FOvernight, Rebekah became a carer to
OL,17,Ftwo young children to stop them from
OL,18,Fgoing into care. She says it was her
OL,19,Fduty as their grandmother, but it was
OL,20,Fa responsibility that she felt came
OL,21,Fwith little support.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772651487
OL,3,CSouth East set to receive millions of
OL,4,Cpounds in funding to help Kinship
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FUntil now, Kinship families did not
OL,8,Fget the same financial help that
OL,9,Ffoster carers do, and they still won't
OL,10,Fbe eligible for an allowance if, like
OL,11,FRebekah, they don't live in one of the
OL,12,Fnew 'Kinship zones.'
OL,14,FRebekah said: "I couldn't even grieve
OL,15,Ffor her because I had to hold onto my
OL,16,Fsanity, otherwise I wouldn't have been
OL,17,Fany good for the two of them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772651487
OL,3,CSouth East set to receive millions of
OL,4,Cpounds in funding to help Kinship
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"We've got a two-bedroom house,
OL,8,Fthere's four of us living here. My son
OL,9,Fhas one bedroom, my grandson has the
OL,10,Fother, grandaughter sleeps here, and I
OL,11,Fsleep on the couch.
OL,13,F"It's great that they are finally
OL,14,Frecognising it, and it's great that
OL,15,Fthese kinship families are getting it,
OL,16,Fbut it should be for everybody because
OL,17,Fwe are all struggling out here."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772651487
OL,3,CSouth East set to receive millions of
OL,4,Cpounds in funding to help Kinship
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FThe #126m government pilot aims to
OL,8,Fsupport around 5,000 Kinship families
OL,9,Fin seven local areas, including Medway
OL,10,Fand Thurrock.
OL,12,FOver the next two years, Medway will
OL,13,Freceive around #16 million pounds in
OL,14,Ffunding, and will support around 300
OL,15,Fvulnerable children and their families.
OL,17,FEach child cared for by a kinship
OL,18,Ffamily will receive around #300 per
OL,19,Fweek. Medway Council says that money
OL,20,Fwill be invaluable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772651487
OL,3,CSouth East set to receive millions of
OL,4,Cpounds in funding to help Kinship
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FIn Thurrock, Katie cared for her
OL,8,Fnephew without that financial backing
OL,9,Fwhen she became a kinship carer at 25.
OL,11,FShe says the support would have made
OL,12,Fher feel less isolated and alone.
OL,14,FKatie said: "Well, obviously, our
OL,15,Fchild is an adult, so it's a bit late
OL,16,Ffor us as a family. And we've had to
OL,17,Fgo through that hardship.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772651487
OL,3,CSouth East set to receive millions of
OL,4,Cpounds in funding to help Kinship
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"It would have been something to work
OL,8,Fwith, to not feel isolated and alone,
OL,9,Flike we have just been left to it, not
OL,10,Ffeel so let down.
OL,12,F"And it would have meant everything
OL,13,Ffor that child to seek support and
OL,14,Fmake things a bit easier."
OL,16,FSome charities say the scheme is an
OL,17,Fimportant milestone in recognising the
OL,18,Fvalue of Kinship carers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772651487
OL,3,CSouth East set to receive millions of
OL,4,Cpounds in funding to help Kinship
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FLucy Peake said: "The government has
OL,8,Frecognised that this system at the
OL,9,Fmoment is not working, it is a
OL,10,Fpostcode lottery, it's a legal lottery
OL,11,Ffor kinship families.
OL,13,F"Many have been struggling, so this
OL,14,Fmarks a real step towards what we
OL,15,Fwant, which is financial support for
OL,16,Fall kinship families."
OL,18,FThe Department for Education hope the
OL,19,Fthree-and-a-half-year pilot will
OL,20,Finform plans for the expansion of
OL,21,FKinship care.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
